The paper deals with robotic navigation and trajectory prediction using Recurrent Neural Networks, which falls under the category of Robotics (cs.RO). The use of RNNs for prediction also involves Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of simulated actions, which could involve Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
